rComments: Why does a public speaking class require a midterm? It was open book though so it's whatever. He's a good prof. Super easy class too. 3 presentations of 3 mins to do and our final was a 7 min presentation too. He posts everything online but takes attendance at times.
You just need to go to class during exam date, he reads his PowerPoint. Impossible to join outside class hours. Not really respectful. DON'T TAKE HIM !
